pos review: Confortable and cozy room, nice host and very nice breakfast, brought to our room at the agreed time. Ten minutes away from the center of Ieper.
Loved the way it was presented, all food was lovely and fresh
Every thing absolutely first class, breakfast was absolutely lovely fresh and plentiful, fresh eggs from Hens in garden.(Which by the way you can not hear.)
good location easy to find,breakfast was excellent delivered on time to the door in basket.Lovely clean room nicely furnished,every thing about place was good 10/10.

The property was lovely.  Very well located about a 10 minute walk from the Menin Gate.  The owners were so nice and very helpful (even let me borrow hair straighteners as I forgot UK/EU adaptor so couldn't use mine). Breakfast was great; delivered outside the room at a time of our choosing and we could eat inside our private room or outside on the most beautiful terrace/garden.  All excellent.
Good location breakfast was nice pascaline and Mark were lovely hosts nothing was to much trouble and the cat was also friendly
neg review: Nothing not to like a great all round stay

pos review: Breakfast was excellent.  Plenty to eat.
